sequenceDiagram
    participant Seller_Bank
    participant Seller_Wallet
    participant Portal
    participant Buyer_Wallet
    participant Buyer_VerifSystem
    participant PSP
    participant PSP_Portal

    critical e-receipt variant1- Datev
    option IBAN
        Buyer_VerifSystem->>+PSP_Portal: send e-Receipt
    option Card
        PSP->>+PSP_Portal: Portal: send e-Receipt
    PSP_Portal->>+Seller_Wallet: send e-Receipt    
    end
    
    critical Send e-receipt variant2- Peppol
    Seller_Bank->>+ Seller_Wallet: Sends payment confirmation
    option Directly
        Seller_Wallet->>+ Buyer_Wallet: Sends e-reciept for e-Invoice
    option over Portal
        Seller_Wallet->>+ Portal: Sends e-reciept for e-Invoice
        Portal->>+ Buyer_Wallet: Sends e-reciept for e-Invoice
    end
